      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_069_000017",
    "sentence": "安國以聞。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_069_000018",
    "sentence": "充國劾安國奉使不敬。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_069_000019",
    "sentence": "是後，羌人旁緣前言，抵冒渡湟水，郡縣不能禁。",
    "entities": [
